        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 3 at 12:03AM CDT until June 3 at 12:45AM CDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>At 1203 AM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Lomax, or 13
miles northwest of Garden City, moving northeast at 40 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Hail damage to vehicles is expected. Expect wind damage to
roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Big Spring, Garden City, Coahoma, Forsan, Sand Springs, Lomax, Big
Spring Country Club, Big Spring McMahon-Wrinkle Airpark, and Elbow.

This includes Interstate 20 between mile markers 165 and 196.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
